parameters:
Jinami Guard: To participate in the arena, you need
qualifications. Please prepare a letter of recommendation
from a skilled warrior.

Jinami Guard: This is... a letter of recommendation from
General Atu!? Welcome to the Pizma Arena, skilled warrior!

Mercenary Captain Gale: What's this? Do you want someone to
punch you?
Will you challenge me to a fight?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then do it)

Clea: You're a participant in the martial arts tournament,
right? Please spar with us.

Mercenary Captain Gale: You're quite confident, young lady.
My honor as a mercenary is at stake, so I won't hold back!

Mercenary Captain Gale: You have impressive skills... I want
you to be in charge of training our new recruits.

Priestess Sophia: In that case, please make the request at
the Adventurer's Guild.

Mercenary Captain Gale: Agonia, the killer of all... I'm not
good with men. If you want to make a request, do it on the
notice board in Oros.
Did you come to me seeking guidance, you arrogant magician?
Will you challenge me to a fight?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then do it)

Clea: You're a participant in the martial arts tournament,
right? Please spar with us.

Arrogant magician: 'You underestimate me... Or perhaps you
can't comprehend my true power?'

Arrogant magician: T-Today, I wasn't feeling well! I'll let
you win this time, so be grateful!
Mage Relm: Hehe, I'll let you have it that way!

Submissive Puppeteer: ...H-hey, hey there, what can I do for
you?
Will you challenge me to a fight?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then do it)

Clea: You're a participant in the martial arts tournament,
right? Please spar with us.

Timid Puppeteer: I-I'll do it...! I'll prove that I'm
strong!

Timid Puppeteer: Ugh, ugh... it's no use, everything I do is
useless...
Thief Nora: D-Don't be so down on yourself!

Proud Man: This is the most exciting city in the empire! The
Pizma Arena is definitely a place worth visiting.

Jinami Guard: This city is the safest place in the empire,
except for the arena.

Jinami Guard: This city is the safest place in the empire,
except for the arena.

Traveling Merchant: Weapons, armor, and consumables, you
know? This is one of the best cities for merchants.

Traveling Merchant: Weapons, armor, and consumables, you
know? This is one of the best cities for merchants.

The boy who aspires to be a warrior says, I'll become strong
enough to participate in the arena someday!

The young boy who aspires to be a warrior said, I saw a
battle! Someday, I'll become strong like my big sister!

A boy who admires warriors says, 'I'll become strong enough
to participate in the arena someday!'

Drunk man: What great weather! Cheers to the resilient king
Pizuma!

Mercenary Leon: I want to eventually make these well-
trained ones known to the world.

Cleric Sophia: She has a very strong physique... Clea-chan!
Doesn't this person seem perfect?
Mercenary Leon: Do you need something from me?

Mercenary Leon: I see, you're looking for a skilled
warrior...

Mercenary Leon: If that's the case, then I'm the perfect
fit. Not to brag, but I'm the most skilled warrior in this
town!

Clea: In that case, could you come with us to the client's
place?
Mercenary Leon: Of course! But there is one condition...

Mercenary Leon: That large sword and that appearance...
You're Clea, the one who defeated the dragon, right?
Clea: That's right, if that's the case, what will happen?

Mercenary Leon: So you really are the real deal... I've
heard the rumors, but to think that such a young girl...

Mercenary Leon: Could you please have a duel with me? I want
to see how far my strength can go against you.
Clea: A duel, huh... I won't hold back.
Mercenary Leon: Thank you! Let me know when you're ready.

Mercenary Leon: I would like to request a duel with the
Dragon Slayer.
Will you engage in a duel with Mercenary Leon?
Mercenary Leon: Let me know when you're ready.
Mercenary Leon: Now, let's have a fair fight!

Mercenary Leon: I'm impressed! Your skills are just as
rumored.

Clea: That was a close match... Leon-san's skills were
amazing!

Mercenary Leon: This will serve as good training. Take this
as a reward!

Mercenary Leon: That was a close match... It seems like I
had a bit of luck on my side.
Clea: I'm defeated... Your swordsmanship was amazing.

Priestess Sophia: Both of you had a splendid battle! With
Leon-san's skills, the client will surely be satisfied.
Clea: Yes, there's no doubt about Mercenary Leon's skills.

Mercenary Leon: We got caught up in the heated battle and
forgot about the main objective. Let's take the client to
their destination right away!
Clea: ...Everyone! I apologize for not giving a report.

Thief Nora: I heard you won! And I received lots of rewards
from Gale-san too!

Mage Relm: We also repelled the thugs! They were scared and
ran away from our strength!
Clea: Thank you very much. Let's return to our journey.
Priestess Sophia: Was it really a good thing...?
Clea: I am still a coward after all.

Clea: Straightforward malice and hostility are also scary. I
thought I had gotten used to it a little through our
adventures.

Clea: But I didn't know that receiving straightforward
kindness could be so scary.
Clea: ...If I become someone else, will I be able to change?
